title: Your (and our) Offseason Goals
description:
The offseason is upon us, which means it's time for all of us to set goals for ourselves and our teams. Will we achieve them? Probably not, but that will not stop us from doing this all again next year. Go Human Brains! Topics on this episode include:
3:21 - The Fullcast hosts as Pokemon types
4:29 - A tribute to a truly great college football hater
15:41 - Your/Our Offseason Goals!
26:57 - What if Dan Mullen poses nude with a shark?
35:12 - Let’s talk about the White House Burger Spread
48:12 - Ok more of Your Offseason Goals
